title: Lesbian serie Girl looks for girl S01E01 (chica busca chica) - T
description:
"Chica busca chica? (Girl looks for Girl) is an online tv show (16 episodes) 
which tells the personal and emotional stories of a bunch of friends that are mostly lesbians. Their
everyday life, job, love, hopes and failures. Girls who look for Girls, searching
for love, searching themselves and who find a lot of troubles.
